'''墨爾本海洋生物水族館'''（'''Sea Life Melbourne Aquarium'''）是一座位於[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[墨爾本|墨爾本]][[亞拉河|亞拉河]]邊的[[水族館|水族館]]，由[[默林娛樂|默林娛樂]]持有。

水族館里不僅包含鯊魚、海龜等海洋生物，也有[[國王企鵝|國王企鵝]]和[[巴布亞企鵝|巴布亞企鵝]]等生物生活的真實冰雪世界。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pta.com.au/web/?page_id=1282|title=Melbourne Aquarium, Stage 2|work=Peddle Thorp Architects|publisher=Peddle Thorp Group|accessdate=2009-07-03|archive-date=2013-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130626123500/http://www.pta.com.au/web/?page_id=1282|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==
墨爾本海洋生物水族館建造于1998年2月至1999年12月間，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://events.frommers.com/sisp/index.htm?fx=event&event_id=99813|title=Melbourne Aquarium|work=Frommer's|publisher=events.frommers.com|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2011-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717071238/http://events.frommers.com/sisp/index.htm?fx=event&event_id=99813|dead-url=no}}</ref> 由[[Peddle_Thorp|Peddle Thorp]]設計，造型模仿的是附在河上的船隻。2000年1月正式開幕。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://au.travel.yahoo.com/great-outdoors/australia/victoria/melbourne/melbourne-aquarium-victoria.html|title=Melbourne Aquarium|work=The Great Outdoors|publisher=[[Yahoo!7|Yahoo!7]]|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2008-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080805142836/http://au.travel.yahoo.com/great-outdoors/australia/victoria/melbourne/melbourne-aquarium-victoria.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該水族館深入街道水平線以下{{Convert|7|m}}，其中心宣稱有是世界最大“圓形海洋水族館”，儲水量為{{Convert|2200000|l|gal|sing=on}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pta.com.au/web/?page_id=1791|title=Melbourne Aquarium, Stage 1|work=Peddle Thorp Architects|publisher=Peddle Thorp Group|accessdate=2009-07-03|archive-date=2014-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228114054/http://www.pta.com.au/web/?page_id=1791|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thatsmelbourne.com.au/Placestogo/Attractions/FamilyFun/Pages/1516.aspx|title=Melbourne Aquarium|work=That's Melbourne|accessdate=2009-07-03|archive-date=2017-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170226153021/http://www.thatsmelbourne.com.au/Placestogo/Attractions/FamilyFun/Pages/1516.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

開幕之後不久的2000年4月11至27日間水族館爆發[[軍團桿菌|軍團桿菌]]感染，導致60人被感染、2人死亡。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/02/02/1075570359810.html|title=Victims of legionnaires' disease win battle|newspaper=[[The_Age|The Age]]|author=Peter Gregory|date=3 February 2004|publisher=[[Fairfax_Media|Fairfax Media]]|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328224159/http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/02/02/1075570359810.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年4月，英國公司[[默林娛樂|默林娛樂]]宣佈將花費800萬美元重新裝修該水族館，同時也將會令水族館更名至默林娛樂旗下。翻新的水族館在同年9月開放。<ref name="2013 relaunch PR">{{Cite press release|title=SEA LIFE Melbourne Aquarium relaunching in September 2013!|url=http://www.melbourneaquarium.com.au/news/relaunch-announcement/|accessdate=12 July 2013|date=23 April 2013|publisher=Melbourne Aquarium|archive-date=2016-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161127153021/https://www.melbourneaquarium.com.au/news/relaunch-announcement/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

